data.description: Spacious 3 bedroom 2 full bath home with great curb appeal.  Room to spread out with both living room and family room each with wall plugs ready to mount your tv's.  Eat in kitchen has large pantry with automatic light an  comes with built in microwave and electric range that was purchased in 2022,  refrigerator and water softener.    You won't run out of hot water as 2nd bath has its own hot water heater for bath and laundry.  Front loading washer and dryer included.  Gas Forced air furnace new in 2023.    Privacy fenced yard, patio and storage shed.  Concrete driveway with motion detector security light on side of home
